`cy.type()` failed because it targeted a disabled element.

The element typed into was:

  > <input class="form-control form-control-lg ng-valid ng-dirty ng-touched" formcontrolname="username" placeholder="Username" type="text">

Ensure the element does not have an attribute named `disabled` before typing into it.

https://on.cypress.io/type
User should have an ability to change username
